{"tid":2513924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"布林肯：對華軍事對抗將嚴重違反中美利益與方向","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:01:37.000Z","uid":278587,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d39db61151ec8483d2f4e91a8aa6f55027157d40","tid":2513924,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588912-20210503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588912-20210503.htm&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=4fcafbeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588912-20210503.htm&h=b2ca4246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588912-20210503.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n七國集團今日起一連三日，在英國倫敦舉行外長會議，英國外相藍韜文表示，會議期間將會與美國國務卿布林肯會面，討論中國及俄羅斯等議題。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，布林肯接受哥倫比亞廣播公司的專訪時表示，如果華府向中國進行軍事對抗，將會嚴重違反中美兩國之間的利益與方向。布林肯表示，中國事實上近期對外採取越來越進取與對抗性行為。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯又表示，美國總統拜登最擔憂的，是中方竊取知識產權問題，強調需要團結理念相近國家，反對北京的不正當競爭行為。中國駐華大使館對專訪未有回應。"},{"pid":"98a8180a7e10330b6e02d097598a773d8bad5e29","tid":2513924,"uid":280136,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>All Talk</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a98de707edabf5e157318a82566ebe5701cc2b8f","tid":2513924,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:26:47.000Z","msg":"幻幻縮了"},{"pid":"732738b96d8f19f859ea075a8eb408ef2b6747f9","tid":2513924,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"露底鳥"},{"pid":"e3d48471f5aa4b81df67fe00963b2bfc4f715c79","tid":2513924,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"仲想和平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908681fe61c692