ehavior-more-aggressive,-increasingly-in-adversarial,-Antony-Blinken-says</a><br />\n<br />\n3 May 2021<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe U.S. Secretary of State Antony Blinken said in an interview that aired on Sunday that China had recently acted &quot;more aggressively abroad&quot; and was behaving &quot;increasingly in adversarial ways,'' Reuters reports.<br />\n<br />\nAsked by CBS News' &quot;60 Minutes&quot; if Washington was heading toward a military confrontation with Beijing, Blinken said: &quot;It's profoundly against the interests of both China and the United States to, to get to that point, or even to head in that direction.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nHe added: &quot;What we've witnessed over the last several years is China acting more repressively at home and more aggressively abroad. That is a fact.&quot;"},{"pid":"754682ad92ff1a5a679a2a5f95de54d9441e9cfe","tid":2513924,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8099cbacb298fa1c312b21fc5d5ecdd11d3c82bb","tid":2513924,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"RTHK 嘅翻譯新聞已經有哂定位, 有無英文來源先?<br />\n就咁睇中文, 佢唔係講緊佢真係好唔想郁手, 叫支那唔好再咁撚過份咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"依句嘢有d怪, <span class=\"red\">&quot;如果華府向中國進行軍事對抗，將會嚴重違反中美兩國之間的利益與方向。布林肯表示，中國事實上近期對外採取越來越進取與對抗性行為&quot;</span>"},{"pid":"70e4973fcd4d453d7d565926ea75115685c05778","tid":2513924,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"又送左幾多櫃幻幻比China joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e825d575980f0b61e21ce254d64596f0dc4ef0","tid":2513924,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"搵到REUTERS原文, 入LINK睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/china/blinken-says-china-acting-more-aggressively-abroad-60-minutes-interview-2021-05-02/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fblinken-says-china-acting-more-aggressively-abroad-60-minutes-interview-2021-05-02%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=f455adc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fblinken-says-china-acting-more-aggressively-abroad-60-minutes-interview-2021-05-02%2F&h=a8e47633\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/blinken-says-china-acting-more-aggressively-abroad-60-minutes-interview-2021-05-02/</a>"},{"pid":"4b3234d16ae67b7bddda6d6a39b4a2e93be9224c","tid":2513924,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Blinken arrived in London on Sunday for a G7 foreign ministers meeting where China is one of the issues on the agenda.<br />\n<br />\nIn the interview, Blinken said the United States was not aiming to &quot;contain China&quot; but to &quot;uphold this rules-based order - that China is posing a challenge to. Anyone who poses a challenge to that order, we're going to stand up and - and defend it.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nBiden has identified competition with China as his administration's greatest foreign policy challenge. In his first speech to Congress last Wednesday, he pledged to maintain a strong U.S. military presence in the Indo-Pacific and to boost U.S. technological development.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我英文真心差, 邊度講美帝縮? <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fe3106f727cb2b7898d6c493cdf5b81b28e095","tid":2513924,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"咁你真係當香港死嘅啫 我哋仲諗住你會用軍事力量製衡中國解放香港"},{"pid":"f91bc2a223cf2812fc6283eedaabfd02903d72f2","tid":2513924,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:47:01.